z3translations.Cmd-参数化简述.Items.ge: Specifies the threshold greater than or equal to the absolute value of item value change to be displayed, defaults to 0

z3translations.Cmd-参数化简述.Items.mode:
Supports "change" (default) or "all", case-insensitive
'change' only shows added, discarded, or changed item data; 'all' is similar to the old version showing items taken in and out
